<p><a name="Catholic" id="Catholic"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Icon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: Catholic">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Catholic</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/07664a.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/07664a.htm" rel="nofollow">"Veneration of Images"</a> article from <i><a href="/wiki/The_Catholic_Encyclopedia" title="The Catholic Encyclopedia" class="mw-redirect">The Catholic Encyclopedia</a></i></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Pictures" id="Pictures"></a></p>
